---
description: Phase-by-phase implementation protocol
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow phased execution from `docs/ADMIN_REBUILD_PHASE_PLAN.md`.

Delivery protocol:
1. Confirm requested phase scope.
2. Implement that phase end-to-end (schema/API/UI/validation).
3. Validate and summarize changes + test steps.
4. Pause for approval before next phase.

Do not partially implement multiple phases in one pass unless user explicitly asks.

